[{"Code":"en","Title":"TH ShopeePay and ShopeePayLater","Slug":"draft-th-shopeepay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a0-gglgnp-851\"><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a0-tm8pno-854\"><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\" display=\"false\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a0-kf2j8q-855\"><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a0-t1gle4-856\"><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-r403yc-857\"><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-xy5g20-858\">Sales/ CS</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05od9-d26w9u-683\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-p18kgo-859\">Submitting the request</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-4ihol9-860\">MO</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-hk6i9j-861\"><a><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut, Kittapat (Pingpong) Srisuphan</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-45vcxa-862\">Request MID and activate channels</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-crb78u-863\">Engineer/ QA</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-nq9il4-864\"><a><u>Mathawat (Bas) Watcharapittayapong</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-i40dtj-865\">Testing MID</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-wr59kv-866\"><a id=\"_7he5vkxzx2mp\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-vax0e7-867\"><a id=\"_ptez5ssmh9h1\" display=\"false\"></a>Partner PIC</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-8ezcqc-868\"><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-d2wmxq-869\"><strong>Email Address</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-vqyj8u-870\"><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a1-yq78f1-871\">ShopeePay Team</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-2efg5g-872\"><a><u>smith.pra@monee.com</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-3f2rwj-873\">Follow up and PIC for MID onboarding</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-gwo91v-874\"><a><u>merchant.service@support.shopeepay.co.th</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-d67urn-875\">When a merchant requests additional channels (e.g., they initially requested ShopeePay but now want to add ShopeePay Later / SPL)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-prnvr7-876\"><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-k8x6in-877\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ssdpg8lh.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-wexuql-878\"><a id=\"_am4yvepyem98\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-6n3g2a-879\"><a id=\"_hbvftyg2k24s\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-e9xwbu-881\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-wbigd9-882\"><strong>Eligible</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-bsvpo3-883\">Sole Proprietorship</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-f41ffu-884\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a2-fptcc4-885\">Corporation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-xnxkvq-886\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-wc9px0-887\">Non-Local Entities</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-lpn7gm-888\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-mi0xpj-889\">Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-rnlsjz-890\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-lhponu-891\">Non-Profit</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-biw8z8-892\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-rhxqtz-893\"><a id=\"_w2g1ajchr0f\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-vp48x0-894\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:371px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"371\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-gpgplb-896\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-ibfcg1-897\"><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"371\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-8n4fj9-898\">Account Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-68na2y-899\">All merchant accounts must be LIVE before applying for ShopeePay activation.</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"371\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-65qfcz-900\">Restricted Industries</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-9p3b53-901\"><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-32v0fz-902\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odf-j9qv5v-684\">Tobacco</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-ikero7-903\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odf-1p59lr-685\">Drugs or medicines</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-f4xjc5-904\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odf-ekv9fy-686\">Illegal products</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-lx2uh0-905\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odf-zu48q2-687\">Gambling</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-61fz8p-906\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odf-vnuras-688\">Infringe products on IP rights</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-atpr0c-907\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odf-qs6gg2-689\">Others that are conflicting with peace and morality of the citizens</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a3-vjsfd5-908\">For more details, you can refer to this sheet: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1J-J4OQ81Ammm6AYTlCgLDVKv0qNIHedHKv5ju6IMhTY/edit?gid=1226972776#gid=1226972776\"><u>TH Partner Prohibited Industry</u></a></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-hczax5-909\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-c6sk1j-910\"><strong>Entity Origin</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-8jp3y2-911\"><strong>SLA</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-llnpho-912\">Local Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-bvwnh6-913\">Instant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-ruohmf-914\">Non-Local (Foreign) Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-4iwkiu-915\">7 to 14 business days</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-u2u8xf-916\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-ypg6pe-917\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-ebm88v-918\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-zts2g0-919\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-5vvje6-920\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-ymmi6a-921\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-6pgfmm-922\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-yblsh2-923\">Merchants submit requests via CS (<a><u>help@xendit.th</u></a>), MO (<a href=\"http://merchantops.th\"><u>merchantops.th</u></a>), or Sales/AM/BD team request for their merchant in<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/CRCJ2E5CK\"> #mo-request</a> and<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/C06338WEJ9M\"> #thailand-pg-activation-request</a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-od7nvt-924\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odh-ur9xqx-690\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a4-unz4c6-925\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-6rq59j-926\">For Xendit merchant, Need to link BID&lt;&gt;GBP in <a href=\"https://retool.gbprimepay.com/apps/63947df6-f23d-11ee-9853-f34fbc3a1698/GB%20Admin%20Dashboard\"><u>Retool link business</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-9f2wu0-927\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odi-qnw9ms-691\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-euggwi-928\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-4w6641-929\">Fill in the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1XXEa0Kg3I7RJvLYtTOJz8Bb0qyvpygL1KfraVt0vtnw/edit?gid=1074778786#gid=1074778786\"><u>required form</u></a>. Ensure all data is ready before the <strong>Thursday cut-off</strong> for the weekly batch submission.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-itazz0-930\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odi-08p6os-692\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-fstf1j-931\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-z1ms6c-932\">Wait for the partner (ShopeePay) to process the whitelist request within the 5-7 business day SLA.</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-w8qcli-933\"><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\" display=\"false\"></a>Activation Flow</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-lrogm3-934\">ShopeePay One-Time Payment</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-xq7l7h-935\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-ifihpr-936\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-v16fr8-937\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-a3kzjq-938\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-364st9-939\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-m0s7hm-940\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-4v7x72-941\">Once the MID is activated on the partner portal, proceed with internal activation using <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/cb87be2c-17f5-11ef-a73d-ffe38ac9a56b/Channel%20Approval/Internal%20Channel%20Activation%20v2\"><u>retool</u></a>.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a5-n64gzh-942\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odk-pcp6vn-693\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-8lrkhm-943\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-mplmpb-944\">Navigate to the Channel Activation Tab, input the merchant’s BID, and select Transaction Entity (Xendit Thailand).</p><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-cv14mr-945\"><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-ry3jtz-946\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bmremb58.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odk-tg1azo-694\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-yg10n1-947\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-krmxrl-948\">Select <strong>EWALLET</strong> as the payment method and <strong>ShopeePay One Time Payment</strong> as the Channel.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-gwdpgm-949\"><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-u53upu-950\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-yteu0oo6.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odl-q2duxx-695\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-32s5ry-951\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-y1cua7-952\">On the next page, input <strong>Merchant’s Name. </strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-vqjbha-953\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-feh8lk-954\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ji09id8q.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odl-0rotgp-696\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-wabva8-955\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-cb7f7p-956\">Click<strong> \"Activate\"</strong> to complete the process.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-ucfmhz-957\"><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-kilunz-958\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-hi2qfked.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-tlj1xl-959\">ShopeePayLater</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-7uachs-961\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-18791l-962\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a6-rrf12o-963\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-0ftn6n-964\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-h90bag-965\">Channel Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-q9mveh-966\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-we64zt-967\">Once the 'SPL Whitelist Status' is updated in the sheet, tag <strong>QA</strong> to test the payment in the requested thread.<br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-57ydyb-972\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ed3qmxkp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-lavsdc-973\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odn-3cggb3-697\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-i1bbb6-974\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-n2ig8i-975\">QA to confirm once SpayLater is already working. Notify the merchant of the result.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-o3abgw-976\"><img data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-kfwwed-977\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bz0drk9r.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-sz924a-978\"><a id=\"_xminc4pn6dqa\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-duedxe-979\"><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\" display=\"false\"></a>Rejection Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-amgr2i-980\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-f8cef6-981\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-2myedv-982\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a7-wko32m-983\"><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odo-u224x9-698\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-7ctcd1-984\">1.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-sod4xz-985\">If a merchant fails onboarding criteria, the MO agent notifies the requester via the original submission channel:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-yjkm8h-986\"><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-kaj68g-987\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odp-wzpgzi-699\">CS: Inform the team to relay the result to the merchant.\t</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-x3t92h-988\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odp-i59k98-700\">Direct MO: Respond to the existing email thread.\t</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-jjfa1w-989\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odp-ojp7wn-701\">Sales/Slack: Reply within the #mo-request or #thailand-pg-activation-request thread.</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmmw84a8-m30s3r-990\">MO</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmt05odp-l4kd7g-702\"></p>","SeoTitle":"TH ShopeePay and ShopeePayLater","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"[Draft] TH ShopeePay","Slug":"draft-th-shopeepay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\"></a>[SOP] TH ShopeePay and ShopeePayLater</p><p><em>Last Update : </em></p><p><em>MO PIC :  </em><a><em><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut</u></em></a></p><h1><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Sales/ CS</p></th><th></th><th><p>Submitting the request</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>MO</p></th><th><p><a><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut</u></a><a><u>Kittapat (Pingpong) Srisuphan</u></a></p></th><th><p>Request MID and activate channels</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Engineer/ QA</p></th><th><p><a><u>Mathawat (Bas) Watcharapittayapong</u></a></p></th><th><p>Testing MID</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_7he5vkxzx2mp\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_ptez5ssmh9h1\"></a>Partner PIC</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Email Address</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>ShopeePay Team</p></th><th><p><a><u>smith.pra@monee.com</u></a></p></th><th><p>Follow up and PIC for MID onboarding</p></th></tr><tr><th><p><a><u>merchant.service@support.shopeepay.co.th</u></a></p></th><th><p>Request for additional channels eg. some merchants are request for SP only at first but want to add SPL.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ssdpg8lh.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_am4yvepyem98\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_hbvftyg2k24s\"></a>Eligibility<br></h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Eligible</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Sole Proprietorship</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Corporation</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Non-Local Entities</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Partnership</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Non-Profit</p></th><th><p>❌</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_w2g1ajchr0f\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\"></a>Merchant Requirements <br></h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Account Status</p></th><th><p>All merchant accounts must be LIVE before applying for ShopeePay activation.</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Restricted Industries</p></th><th><ul><li>Tobacco</li><li>Drugs or medicines</li><li>Illegal products</li><li>Gambling</li><li>Infringe products on IP rights</li><li>Others that are conflicting with peace and morality of the citizens</li></ul><p>For more details, you can refer to this sheet: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1J-J4OQ81Ammm6AYTlCgLDVKv0qNIHedHKv5ju6IMhTY/edit?gid=1226972776#gid=1226972776\"><u>TH Partner Prohibited Industry</u></a></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\"></a>SLA</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Entity Origin</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>SLA</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local Entity</p></th><th><p>Instant</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Non-Local (Foreign) Entity</p></th><th><p>7 to 14 business days</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Merchants submit requests via CS (<a><u>help@xendit.th</u></a>), MO (<a href=\"http://merchantops.th\"><u>merchantops.th</u></a>), or Sales/AM/BD team request for their merchant in<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/CRCJ2E5CK\"> #mo-request</a> and<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/C06338WEJ9M\"> #thailand-pg-activation-request</a></p></th><th><p>Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3</p></th><th><p>For Xendit merchant, Need to link BID&lt;&gt;GBP in <a href=\"https://retool.gbprimepay.com/apps/63947df6-f23d-11ee-9853-f34fbc3a1698/GB%20Admin%20Dashboard\"><u>Retool link business</u></a></p></th><th><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>Fill in the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1XXEa0Kg3I7RJvLYtTOJz8Bb0qyvpygL1KfraVt0vtnw/edit?gid=1074778786#gid=1074778786\"><u>required form</u></a>. Ensure all data is ready before the <strong>Thursday cut-off</strong> for the weekly batch submission.</p></th><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>Wait for the partner (ShopeePay) to process the whitelist request within the 5-7 business day SLA.</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\"></a>Activation Flow</h1><p>ShopeePay One-Time Payment</p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Once the MID is activated on the partner portal, proceed with internal activation using <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/cb87be2c-17f5-11ef-a73d-ffe38ac9a56b/Channel%20Approval/Internal%20Channel%20Activation%20v2\"><u>retool</u></a>.</p></th><th rowspan=\"5\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>Navigate to the Channel Activation Tab, input the merchant’s BID, and select Transaction Entity (Xendit Thailand).</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bmremb58.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3</p></th><th><p>Select <strong>EWALLET</strong> as the payment method and <strong>ShopeePay One Time Payment</strong> as the Channel.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-yteu0oo6.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>On the next page, input <strong>Merchant’s Name. </strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ji09id8q.png\"></strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>5</p></th><th><p>Click<strong> \"Activate\"</strong> to complete the process.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-hi2qfked.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><p>ShopeePayLater<br></p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Once the 'SPL Whitelist Status' is updated in the sheet, tag <strong>QA</strong> to test the payment in the requested thread.<br><br><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ed3qmxkp.png\"></p></th><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>QA to confirm once SpayLater is already working. Notify the merchant of the result.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bz0drk9r.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_xminc4pn6dqa\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\"></a>Rejection Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>1.</p></th><th><p>If a merchant fails onboarding criteria, the MO agent notifies the requester via the original submission channel:</p><ul><li>CS: Inform the team to relay the result to the merchant.\t</li><li>Direct MO: Respond to the existing email thread.\t</li><li>Sales/Slack: Reply within the #mo-request or #thailand-pg-activation-request thread.</li></ul></th><th><p>MO</p></th></tr></thead></table>","SeoTitle":"[Draft] TH ShopeePay","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"[Draft] TH ShopeePay","Slug":"draft-th-shopeepay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\"></a>[SOP] TH ShopeePay and ShopeePayLater</p><p><em>Last Update : </em></p><p><em>MO PIC :  </em><a><em><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut</u></em></a></p><h1><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Sales/ CS</p></th><th></th><th><p>Submitting the request</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>MO</p></th><th><p><a><u>Kavissara (Praew)