e products on IP rights</li><li>Others that are conflicting with peace and morality of the citizens</li></ul><p>For more details, you can refer to this sheet: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1J-J4OQ81Ammm6AYTlCgLDVKv0qNIHedHKv5ju6IMhTY/edit?gid=1226972776#gid=1226972776\"><u>TH Partner Prohibited Industry</u></a></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\"></a>SLA</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Entity Origin</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>SLA</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Local Entity</p></th><th><p>Instant</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Non-Local (Foreign) Entity</p></th><th><p>7 to 14 business days</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Merchants submit requests via CS (<a><u>help@xendit.th</u></a>), MO (<a href=\"http://merchantops.th\"><u>merchantops.th</u></a>), or Sales/AM/BD team request for their merchant in<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/CRCJ2E5CK\"> #mo-request</a> and<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/C06338WEJ9M\"> #thailand-pg-activation-request</a></p></th><th><p>Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3</p></th><th><p>For Xendit merchant, Need to link BID&lt;&gt;GBP in <a href=\"https://retool.gbprimepay.com/apps/63947df6-f23d-11ee-9853-f34fbc3a1698/GB%20Admin%20Dashboard\"><u>Retool link business</u></a></p></th><th><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>Fill in the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1XXEa0Kg3I7RJvLYtTOJz8Bb0qyvpygL1KfraVt0vtnw/edit?gid=1074778786#gid=1074778786\"><u>required form</u></a>. Ensure all data is ready before the <strong>Thursday cut-off</strong> for the weekly batch submission.</p></th><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>Wait for the partner (ShopeePay) to process the whitelist request within the 5-7 business day SLA.</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\"></a>Activation Flow</h1><p>ShopeePay One-Time Payment</p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Once the MID is activated on the partner portal, proceed with internal activation using <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/cb87be2c-17f5-11ef-a73d-ffe38ac9a56b/Channel%20Approval/Internal%20Channel%20Activation%20v2\"><u>retool</u></a>.</p></th><th rowspan=\"5\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>Navigate to the Channel Activation Tab, input the merchant’s BID, and select Transaction Entity (Xendit Thailand).</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bmremb58.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3</p></th><th><p>Select <strong>EWALLET</strong> as the payment method and <strong>ShopeePay One Time Payment</strong> as the Channel.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-yteu0oo6.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>On the next page, input <strong>Merchant’s Name. </strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ji09id8q.png\"></strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>5</p></th><th><p>Click<strong> \"Activate\"</strong> to complete the process.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-hi2qfked.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><p>ShopeePayLater<br></p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Once the 'SPL Whitelist Status' is updated in the sheet, tag <strong>QA</strong> to test the payment in the requested thread.<br><br><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ed3qmxkp.png\"></p></th><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>QA to confirm once SpayLater is already working. Notify the merchant of the result.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bz0drk9r.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_xminc4pn6dqa\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\"></a>Rejection Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>1.</p></th><th><p>If a merchant fails onboarding criteria, the MO agent notifies the requester via the original submission channel:</p><ul><li>CS: Inform the team to relay the result to the merchant.\t</li><li>Direct MO: Respond to the existing email thread.\t</li><li>Sales/Slack: Reply within the #mo-request or #thailand-pg-activation-request thread.</li></ul></th><th><p>MO</p></th></tr></thead></table>","SeoTitle":"[Draft] TH ShopeePay","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"[Draft] TH ShopeePay","Slug":"draft-th-shopeepay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\"></a>[SOP] TH ShopeePay and ShopeePayLater</p><p><em>Last Update : </em></p><p><em>MO PIC :  </em><a><em><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut</u></em></a></p><h1><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Sales/ CS</p></th><th></th><th><p>Submitting the request</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>MO</p></th><th><p><a><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut</u></a><a><u>Kittapat (Pingpong) Srisuphan</u></a></p></th><th><p>Request MID and activate channels</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Engineer/ QA</p></th><th><p><a><u>Mathawat (Bas) Watcharapittayapong</u></a></p></th><th><p>Testing MID</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_7he5vkxzx2mp\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_ptez5ssmh9h1\"></a>Partner PIC</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Email Address</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>ShopeePay Team</p></th><th><p><a><u>smith.pra@monee.com</u></a></p></th><th><p>Follow up and PIC for MID onboarding</p></th></tr><tr><th><p><a><u>merchant.service@support.shopeepay.co.th</u></a></p></th><th><p>Request for additional channels eg. some merchants are request for SP only at first but want to add SPL.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ssdpg8lh.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_am4yvepyem98\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_hbvftyg2k24s\"></a>Eligibility<br></h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Eligible</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Sole Proprietorship</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Corporation</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Non-Local Entities</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Partnership</p></th><th><p>✅</p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Non-Profit</p></th><th><p>❌</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_w2g1ajchr0f\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\"></a>Merchant Requirements <br></h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Account Status</p></th><th><p>All merchant accounts must be LIVE before applying for ShopeePay activation.</p>