efore the <strong>Thursday cut-off</strong> for the weekly batch submission.</p></th><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>Wait for the partner (ShopeePay) to process the whitelist request within the 5-7 business day SLA.</p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\"></a>Activation Flow</h1><p>ShopeePay One-Time Payment</p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Once the MID is activated on the partner portal, proceed with internal activation using <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/cb87be2c-17f5-11ef-a73d-ffe38ac9a56b/Channel%20Approval/Internal%20Channel%20Activation%20v2\"><u>retool</u></a>.</p></th><th rowspan=\"5\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>Navigate to the Channel Activation Tab, input the merchant’s BID, and select Transaction Entity (Xendit Thailand).</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bmremb58.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>3</p></th><th><p>Select <strong>EWALLET</strong> as the payment method and <strong>ShopeePay One Time Payment</strong> as the Channel.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-yteu0oo6.png\"></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>4</p></th><th><p>On the next page, input <strong>Merchant’s Name. </strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ji09id8q.png\"></strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>5</p></th><th><p>Click<strong> \"Activate\"</strong> to complete the process.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-hi2qfked.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><p>ShopeePayLater<br></p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th><p>Channel Activation</p></th><th><p>1</p></th><th><p>Once the 'SPL Whitelist Status' is updated in the sheet, tag <strong>QA</strong> to test the payment in the requested thread.<br><br><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-ed3qmxkp.png\"></p></th><th rowspan=\"2\"><p>MO</p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>2</p></th><th><p>QA to confirm once SpayLater is already working. Notify the merchant of the result.</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-th-shopeepay-image-bz0drk9r.png\"></p></th></tr></thead></table><h1><a id=\"_xminc4pn6dqa\"></a></h1><h1><a id=\"_eo8f2o4hqql8\"></a>Rejection Flow</h1><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>No</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Owner / PIC </strong></p></th></tr><tr><th></th><th><p>1.</p></th><th><p>If a merchant fails onboarding criteria, the MO agent notifies the requester via the original submission channel:</p><ul><li>CS: Inform the team to relay the result to the merchant.\t</li><li>Direct MO: Respond to the existing email thread.\t</li><li>Sales/Slack: Reply within the #mo-request or #thailand-pg-activation-request thread.</li></ul></th><th><p>MO</p></th></tr></thead></table>","SeoTitle":"[Draft] TH ShopeePay","Description":null}]